Here's an example of how you can modify your JavaScript code to ensure it runs after the document is fully loaded:

```javascript
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    // Your existing JavaScript code here
    const moneyDisplay = document.getElementById('moneydisplay');
    // The rest of your code that uses moneyDisplay
});
```

